Use RefManageR_0.14.20.tar\RefManageR\vignettes
Maybe checkout RefManageR::ReadPDFs
Maybe checkout RefManageR::SearchBib

Maybe checkout RefManageR::ReadCrossRef
Checkout the api on https://github.com/CrossRef/rest-api-doc

You can likely do something like the following to get information from the .bib file
library(RefManageR)
file.name <- system.file("Bib", "biblatexExamples.bib", package = "RefManageR")
bib <- ReadBib(file.name, check = FALSE)

bib[author = "westfahl"][[1]]$publisher